                        <interp inst="t18371127-name-545" type="occupation" value="omnibus driver"></interp>
                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t18371127-92-offence-1 t18371127-name-545"></join>James Bramble</persName>; and that he had been before convicted of felony.</rs>
